{"tid":2454546,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王婆婆給何桂藍、朱凱廸的信ー「最後沒有去警署見你和亞藍，內心裏很難過」","createTime":"2021-03-20T10:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T15:55:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"200916dfe016307add99fa773a70cce653fc0e52","tid":2454546,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5536&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDFlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=f608c71b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5536</a><br />\n<br />\n/王婆婆在袋中，拿出兩封尚未送給朱凱迪及何桂藍的信，上面寫著「在被拘留前一天，我並沒有去八鄉警署見你和亞藍，內心裏很難過。」她說「其實最掛念他們兩人，因為認識較久，有很多事情上曾經幫助過我。」<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆訴說著，與何桂藍識於微時，由雨傘運動至今，細數已有七年，當時的何桂藍還是一個學生記者。王婆婆稱「（何桂藍）同2014年一樣，都係咁靚女。」兩人相識多時，在王婆婆心目中的何桂藍是個「叻女」，稱讚她「文筆又唔錯，又勤力，人緣都幾好」。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱迪在王婆婆失蹤一年裏，曾連同其他民主派議員寄出電郵與她聯繫，在郵件中告知王婆婆有許多港人在掛念她。王婆婆憶起當時，只能在深圳的圖書館，偷偷摸摸地撰寫郵件或短訊給朱凱迪，過程歷時一年多，「如果唔係我都撐唔到，可能死喺深圳。」王婆婆感激朱凱廸及張超雄的幫助，百忙之中仍然通知她最新消息並送上慰問。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆未能到八鄉警署見見他們，心裏有一份悔疚，沒有想過那天以後，便已一牆相隔。王婆婆表示很想探望二人，並親口說出這份苦衷，更希望何桂藍與朱凱迪的探訪名單上，能加上「王鳳瑤」這個名字。<br />\n<br />\n其實在拍攝過程中，王婆婆一聽見任何風吹草動，便會立即回頭，看看是否還有其他囚車駛出，她就是如此心繫每位「手足」，害怕錯過那僅餘的空間和時間送上支持。王婆婆很健談的，若果你在現場看到她，不妨與她聊聊天。若然知道路上有人結伴而行，她會很高興的。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfeature.com/%e4%ba%ba%e7%89%a9%e5%b0%88%e8%a8%aa/%e7%8e%8b%e5%a9%86%e5%a9%86%e7%b5%a6%e4%bd%95%e6%a1%82%e8%97%8d%e3%80%81%e6%9c%b1%e5%87%b1%e5%bb%b8%e7%9a%84%e4%bf%a1%e3%83%bc%e3%80%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%be%8c%e6%b2%92%e6%9c%89%e5%8e%bb%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2/14050/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfeature.com%2F%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2589%25a9%25e5%25b0%2588%25e8%25a8%25aa%2F%25e7%258e%258b%25e5%25a9%2586%25e5%25a9%2586%25e7%25b5%25a6%25e4%25bd%2595%25e6%25a1%2582%25e8%2597%258d%25e3%2580%2581%25e6%259c%25b1%25e5%2587%25b1%25e5%25bb%25b8%25e7%259a%2584%25e4%25bf%25a1%25e3%2583%25bc%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%259c%2580%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%25b2%2592%25e6%259c%2589%25e5%258e%25bb%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25bd%25b2%2F14050%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDFlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=a5a6bd3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfeature.com/%e4%ba%ba%e7%89%a9%e5%b0%88%e8%a8%aa/%e7%8e%8b%e5%a9%86%e5%a9%86%e7%b5%a6%e4%bd%95%e6%a1%82%e8%97%8d%e3%80%81%e6%9c%b1%e5%87%b1%e5%bb%b8%e7%9a%84%e4%bf%a1%e3%83%bc%e3%80%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%be%8c%e6%b2%92%e6%9c%89%e5%8e%bb%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2/14050/</a>"},{"pid":"9223a93b0d1f29478f5ef397d3b9b631c349aba9","tid":2454546,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd20cf00f48fbeb6734fce80c71d34483fdc6296","tid":2454546,"uid":276191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"感激王婆婆&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b7275ecc74f5974967b1fcd45ce004ddda8fd2","tid":2454546,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d3460a588ca768609e1f8127b84ce3fbce863a","tid":2454546,"uid":325346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"經歷左咁多最硬的是佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e5d077e94698dafa18ff7254ca088a6527c290","tid":2454546,"uid":55162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"王婆婆真係好錫d後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你平安"},{